The right experience.Perspective that sorts it all out.





What we do
Mohanty Gargiulo LLC is a financial advisory firm with the mission to deliver best-in-class derivatives and structured products advice to public, not-for-profit, corporate entities, and institutional investors.


Our objective
Our goal is to enable informed decision making through comprehensive and objective advice developed in the context of our clients’ business and priorities, as well as market realities.


Our competitive edge
Our analytical lens was developed from decades of experience in banking and issuer and investor derivatives, creating a perspective that brings all of the pieces together.




