Our Process
Creating clear context for derivative and structured products within an entire portfolio of a particular enterprise is the goal of our process. As a result, we believe that each client should understand their current portfolio and the dynamics of this portfolio as a start. Using this context combined with the client’s financing objectives will provide a better foundation for analyzing the benefits and exposures of any potential product.









